{"tid":750602,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[袁生]今日終於睇咗粉紅傳第一集","createTime":"2018-07-21T04:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T17:18:50.000Z","uid":191041,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e25d15ca101cddc2753ca416049a219f648250","tid":750602,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:47:08.000Z","msg":"正所謂知己知彼 成日笑佢同時又未睇過 又難免有失公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我心血來潮睇咗一集 果然係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始先嚟個彩頁 想學日本啲漫畫 嚟個先聲奪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畫功就不再講 哇 啲人嘅比例呢 勁過足球小將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲對白呢 仲正過tvb 正常人都唔會講得出囗<br />\n劇情啦喎 公道啲講句第一集有乜劇情呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之就一路睇一路笑 袁生應該改畫搞笑漫畫就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bec9ffd02ad66c4b6082654c67bc44da098dacf","tid":750602,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"你識條春咩"},{"pid":"8309693a62945f1f28aae33b500f58106846e021","tid":750602,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bec9ffd02ad66c4b6082654c67bc44da098dacf","tid":750602,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"你識條春咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"我的確唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098feabbf5ff9a205a8ab4d3cc4f3ce7f27e8b4e","tid":750602,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"良心有愧...."},{"pid":"2eb4bf748f8a16d8d49548e692615b709a98dbf7","tid":750602,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098feabbf5ff9a205a8ab4d3cc4f3ce7f27e8b4e","tid":750602,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:43:37.000Z","msg"